videos.headline: Mitchell makes leaping grab in end zone for Bulldogs TD
videos.description: Mississippi State QB Tommy Stevens goes deep and finds Osirus Mitchell who rises up in traffic for the 28-yard touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Mitchell makes leaping grab in end zone for Bulldogs TD) 2019/09/07

videos.headline: Gibson untouched on 13-yard Mississippi State TD
videos.description: Bulldogs RB Nick Gibson bursts through the middle and easily finds paydirt to give Mississippi State a 21-0 lead just before the half.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Gibson untouched on 13-yard Mississippi State TD) 2019/09/07

videos.headline: Mississippi State scores on Stevens-to-Guidry connection
videos.description: Tommy Stevens throws over the middle to Stephen Guidry for an 11-yard touchdown, putting Mississippi State ahead 14-0.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Mississippi State scores on Stevens-to-Guidry connection) 2019/09/07

videos.headline: Hill powers into end zone for Mississippi State TD
videos.description: Bulldogs RB Kylin Hill gets past a defender at the goal line and scores from three yards out to give Mississippi State a commanding 28-0 lead.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Hill powers into end zone for Mississippi State TD) 2019/09/07

videos.headline: Southern Miss WR lays out for stellar TD grab
videos.description: Jack Abraham airs it out for Jaylond Adams who makes a diving catch in the end zone for a 28-yard score to put Southern Mississippi on the board.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Southern Miss WR lays out for stellar TD grab) 2019/09/07

videos.headline: Bulldogs break out turnover dog collar after INT
videos.description: Mississippi State freshman Martin Emerson comes up with an interception on defense and is rewarded with the team's turnover dog collar.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Bulldogs break out turnover dog collar after INT) 2019/09/07

videos.headline: Mississippi State freshman Witherspoon gets 1st-career TD
videos.description: Bulldogs RB Lee Witherspoon breaks loose for a 22-yard touchdown, marking the first score of his collegiate career.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Mississippi State freshman Witherspoon gets 1st-career TD) 2019/09/07
